      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+1\n\n(5 comments)\n\nI think converting nearby lines to tabs as we go along will reduce the total number of patches, and is a no-op w.r.t. upstream patches since the upstream client code already has done the space->tab conversion.  Otherwise, we need to add another patch that does only whitespace conversion and that will cause gratuitous conflicts with other patches that are making actual improvements to the code.",
